"{\"uid\": \"torrentfreak.com-ioc-sends-thousands-of-dmca-notices-to-deter-olympics-piracy-240731\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home>Piracy> The International Olympic Committee is working around the clock to protect its broadcasting rights.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 49, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Home>Piracy\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 11}, {\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"its broadcasting rights\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past week, IOC has sent thousands of DMCA takedown notices to Google.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notice_and_take_down\", \"score\": 0.999951752525497, \"rank\": 4.824980226488339e-05, \"text\": \"DMCA takedown\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notice_and_take_down\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notice_and_take_down\"}, {\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"score\": 0.9996132939541402, \"rank\": 0.000386855644983213, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past week\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They reveal that torrent sites are a problem of the past; live-streaming sites are the main concern now.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"torrent sites\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"live-streaming sites\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"the main concern\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) is known to be very protective of its intellectual property rights.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its intellectual property rights\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using an image of the Olympic rings or even just the word 'Olympic' can lead to legal trouble, especially when use takes place in a commercial context.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an image\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"legal trouble\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"a commercial context\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most valuable, however, are IOC's broadcasting rights.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With literally billions of dollars at stake, the IOC and its licensing partners are doing everything in their power to prevent people from enjoying their events without permission.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"literally billions\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"dollars\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"stake\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"its licensing partners\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"their power\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"their events\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC does not shy away from using its power and influence to aid this cause.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its power\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"influence\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"this cause\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sixteen years ago, for example, itreached out to the Swedish Government, asking for assistance to remove pirated Olympic broadcasts from The Pirate Bay.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Sweden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Swedish Government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"assistance\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"pirated Olympic broadcasts\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"The Pirate Bay\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sweden could not directly help with this problem, as it lacked any control over the notorious torrent site.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.999990301195534, \"rank\": 9.698788969913912e-06, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this problem\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"any control\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"the notorious torrent site\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Pirate Bay itself did not feel threatened by the diplomatic pressure either.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Pirate Bay\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"the diplomatic pressure\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, it temporarily renamed itself The Beijing Bay.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrary\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"The Beijing Bay\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, Olympic piracy remains a problem, but the nature of the threat has evolved.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic piracy\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"the nature\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"the threat\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of worrying about torrents, the IOC sees live-streaming portals as themenace du jour.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"torrents\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"live-streaming portals\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"themenace du jour\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike torrents, which can take a while to download, live streams directly compete with regular broadcasts.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"torrents\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"live streams\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"regular broadcasts\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, we already reported that the IOC, alongside others, obtained asite blocking orderat the Paris Judicial Court.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999992627165728, \"rank\": 7.372839176013594e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"asite blocking orderat\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This order requires the large French ISPs to block access to several pirate streaming sites and IPTV providers.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999338307617468, \"rank\": 4.478046883592245e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This order\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"several pirate streaming sites\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"IPTV providers\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the blocking order is currently in effect, it is limited to 25 domain names and only applies to France.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"score\": 0.5561453075373034, \"rank\": 0.7944710850847909, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the blocking order\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"effect\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"25 domain names\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Committee did not stop there though, it also enlisted anti-piracy partnerFriend MTSto issue more traditional DMCA takedown requests.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2041, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notice_and_take_down\", \"score\": 0.999951752525497, \"rank\": 4.824980226488339e-05, \"text\": \"DMCA takedown\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notice_and_take_down\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Notice_and_take_down\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of these DMCA efforts take place outside the public eye.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_Millennium_Copyright_Act\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DMCA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_Millennium_Copyright_Act\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_Millennium_Copyright_Act\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"the public eye\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With help from Google'stransparency reportand theLumen Database, we can nonetheless get a glimpse of the takedown action.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"Google'stransparency reportand theLumen Database\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"a glimpse\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"the takedown action\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These public data reveal that IOC has sent numerous takedown notices this month, together targeting thousands of URLs.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2281, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These public data\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous takedown notices\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"URLs\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The notices request Google to remove these links from its search engine, to make it harder for the public to find pirated Olympics streams.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2390, \"end\": 2396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"score\": 0.9996132939541402, \"rank\": 0.000386855644983213, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The notices\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"these links\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"its search engine\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"pirated Olympics streams\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Please note that the IOC is the owner of all rights in and to the Olympic Games and the Olympic Properties and, in particular, regarding the audio-visual content produced for the Olympic Summer Games Paris 2024,\\\" IOC writes \\\"Such Olympic content may not be transmitted or communicated via the internet or any other interactive media or electronic medium without the express prior written approval of the IOC, which in accordance with our records, has not been granted to you.\\\"\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2533, \"end\": 2536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2725, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2917, \"end\": 2920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the owner\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"all rights\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2591}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Properties\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"the audio-visual content\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Summer Games Paris\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"Such Olympic content\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the internet\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"any other interactive media\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"electronic medium\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"the express prior written approval\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"accordance\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"our records\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thus far, the IOC has asked Google to remove 5,907 URLs from its search engine.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3007, \"end\": 3010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3021, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"score\": 0.9996132939541402, \"rank\": 0.000386855644983213, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"5,907 URLs\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"its search engine\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The list is dominated by pirate streaming sites such as Antenasports.ru, Buff-streams.net, Francemag.com, and Watchsportnow.com.\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The list\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"pirate streaming sites\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"Antenasports.ru\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"Buff-streams.net\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"Francemag.com\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"Watchsportnow.com\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interestingly, we did not spot a single torrent site.\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a single torrent site\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Due to the delayed nature of torrents and direct downloads, in combination with widely available pirated live streams, it makes sense that sites such as The Pirate Bay are no longer considered a significant threat.\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the delayed nature\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3282}, {\"ngram\": \"torrents\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3294}, {\"ngram\": \"direct downloads\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"combination\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"widely available pirated live streams\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3374}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3390}, {\"ngram\": \"sites\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"The Pirate Bay\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant threat\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, aside from the opening ceremony, we have not spotted any regularly scheduled 'torrents' of Olympic competitions.\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3480}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"any regularly scheduled 'torrents\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic competitions\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a far cry from a decade ago when theoriginal EZTV teamopenly revolted against IOC's anti-piracy tactics by sharing numerous Olympic torrents.\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3647, \"end\": 3651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EZTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5807572778774467e-27, \"text\": \"EZTV\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EZTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EZTV\"}, {\"begin\": 3680, \"end\": 3683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a far cry\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous Olympic torrents\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[T]he IOC is purely interested in making as much money from broadcasting as possible.\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3752, \"end\": 3755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.222884870313458e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as much money\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We think differently, we believe everyone should be able to see these events freely and inspire future sport heroes!\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3873}, {\"ngram\": \"these events\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"future sport heroes\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"EZTV told usat the time.\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"EZTV\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3953}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 3972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fast-forward a decade, and the new EZTV team has no Olympic coverage and there is no \\\"Paris Bay\\\" either.\", \"from\": 3975, \"to\": 4079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4010, \"